ktexteditorpreviewplugin: KTextEditor Document Preview Plugin
ktexteditorpreviewplugin:
ktexteditorpreviewplugin: A plugin for the editor Kate, the IDE KDevelop, or other software
ktexteditorpreviewplugin: using the KTextEditor framework.
ktexteditorpreviewplugin:
ktexteditorpreviewplugin: This plugin enables a live preview of the currently edited text
ktexteditorpreviewplugin: document in the final format.
ktexteditorpreviewplugin:
ktexteditorpreviewplugin: For the display it uses the KParts plugin which is currently
ktexteditorpreviewplugin: selected as the preferred one for the MIME type of the document.
ktexteditorpreviewplugin: If there is no matching KParts plugin, no preview is possible.
